data.description: Welcome to 418 Garland Drive, Unit 227, a charming 2-bedroom, 2-bath condo that effortlessly combines style with convenience. Newly refurbished with luxury vinyl flooring and fresh paint, this  place offers a contemporary and inviting ambiance.    Situated in a prime location, this condo boasts easy access to several manufacturing plants, making it ideal for professionals seeking a seamless work-life balance. With a variety of shopping centers just moments away, indulging in retail therapy, great restaurants, and meeting daily needs has never been more convenient. The allure of Surfside Beach, is a short drive away, promising endless opportunities for relaxation & recreation.    Designed for practical living, this unit comes complete with a stackable washer/dryer, providing the utmost convenience for your day-to-day activities.    Discover the perfect blend of comfort, style, and accessibility at 418 Garland Drive, Unit 227. Don't miss the chance to make this cozy condo your next home.
